{{about|the historical Communist Party of the Soviet Union|the union of communist parties from the former Soviet Union|Union of Communist Parties — Communist Party of the Soviet Union}}
{{Infobox Political Party
|colorcode= red
|native_name= Коммунистическая  партия Советского Союза (Kommunisticheskaya partiya Sovetskovo Soyuza)
|name= Communist Party of the Soviet Union
|party_logo= [[File:Pin of the Flag of CPSU.png]]
