      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox CVG system
|title = Telstar
|logo =
|image= [[Image:ctelstar.jpg]]
|manufacturer= [[Coleco]]
|type= [[Dedicated console]]
|generation= [[History of video game consoles (first generation)|First generation]]
