===Creation from chaos===
{{main|Chaos (cosmogony)}}
In creation from chaos myth, initially there is nothing but a formless, shapeless expanse.  In these stories the word &quot;chaos&quot; means &quot;disorder&quot;, and this formless expanse, which is also sometimes called a void or an abyss